    "description": "The 330G2 is an ISO 7816 and GSC-IS compliant cryptographic smart card designed for identification and access control applications. The card provides a secure, mobile platform for creating, storing and using keys, certificates, passwords and other digital credentials. Security services include: Multiapplication secure storage and retrieval of data and digital credentials. Authentication of the cardholder and the security officer. Cryptographic services including SHA-1, DES, 3DES, RSA Sign/Verify, RSA Encrypt/Decrypt and DSA Sign/Verify with on board key generation including RSA 2048-bit key generation.",
